00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:18.640
Why are you locked up here?

00:00:22.559 --> 00:00:23.359
Man'er.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:26.640
Truly impressive.

00:00:27.719 --> 00:00:29.960
I must have good karma
in several lifetimes

00:00:30.359 --> 00:00:32.439
to marry a woman like you,

00:00:33.079 --> 00:00:35.240
an exceptionally intelligent
and extraordinary woman.

00:00:37.159 --> 00:00:38.920
So what if I'm clever?

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:43.520
I still can't hold a man's heart.

00:00:45.159 --> 00:00:46.920
Your heart

00:00:47.320 --> 00:00:49.240
is full of countless distractions.

00:00:49.960 --> 00:00:51.560
I can't even count them all.

00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:56.359
Those distractions will
wither sooner or later.

00:00:56.880 --> 00:00:58.039
Unlike you,

00:00:58.479 --> 00:01:00.240
you are pure gold.

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:02.880
Smart, capable

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:04.159
and determined.

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:08.040
I must hold you tightly in my hand.

00:01:08.519 --> 00:01:09.840
It seems the Xiao family

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.640
will return to our hands eventually.

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:15.319
Your determination

00:01:15.719 --> 00:01:17.280
makes me feel inferior.

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:18.680
If

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.439
it weren't you

00:01:20.439 --> 00:01:22.959
putting the spices into
the Grand Madam's incense burner,

00:01:23.359 --> 00:01:25.400
how could things have gone so smoothly?

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:27.840
The old woman had no real issue,

00:01:28.319 --> 00:01:29.560
what kind of determination is that?

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:34.400
You would
even sacrifice your own mother.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:36.680
Surely one day,

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.519
you will sell me out too.

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:44.480
Man'er.

00:01:45.519 --> 00:01:46.599
With you,

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:48.120
I can have all of this.

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:50.439
Even if I'm foolish,

00:01:50.760 --> 00:01:51.799
I wouldn't

00:01:51.959 --> 00:01:53.920
do such a stupid, short-sighted thing.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:29.159
People in the residence say

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:31.199
Xiao Ye and Su Man'er claim that Madam

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:33.120
poisoned Grand Madam Xiao with incense,

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.960
then locked Madam in the woodshed.

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.759
Has anyone been sent
to check the incense?

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:37.580
They have been checked.

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:39.560
I'll go back and see.

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:40.199
Let's go.

00:02:40.199 --> 00:02:40.719
General!

00:02:41.759 --> 00:02:42.560
General, Qing Yan...

00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:43.280
I already know.

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:44.400
Come with me.

00:02:44.919 --> 00:02:46.479
I guarantee she will be safe.

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:50.639
You also locked Yun Juan up.

00:02:54.719 --> 00:02:55.919
You can't forget her,

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:57.919
then I'll just bring her back.

00:02:58.280 --> 00:02:59.719
Man'er.

00:03:00.719 --> 00:03:02.080
What nonsense are you saying?

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:03.719
I've long grown tired of her.

00:03:04.479 --> 00:03:06.199
If not for my old mother,

00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:08.360
I would've sold her off already.

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:10.719
Even though she
did a great deed this time,

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:12.560
I must let her know

00:03:13.039 --> 00:03:15.599
who is the true master
of the Second Master's household.

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.280
I just worry

00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:20.319
about locking her up with Qing Yan

00:03:21.319 --> 00:03:21.930
is not appropriate.

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:26.280
What if she exposes me?

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.159
You don't expose him

00:03:28.719 --> 00:03:30.080
because you love him.

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:33.439
You married the General,

00:03:33.719 --> 00:03:35.159
became the General's wife,

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:37.319
naturally confident to do as you please.

00:03:37.639 --> 00:03:39.719
I don't become the General's wife

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:41.919
to do whatever I want.

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:45.159
I follow my heart first

00:03:45.919 --> 00:03:47.639
that allows me to become
the General's wife.

00:03:50.439 --> 00:03:52.360
Once you face family punishment,

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:54.479
I'll be promoted to a concubine.

00:03:54.479 --> 00:03:55.520
Then

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:57.520
I will naturally have confidence.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:59.280
General's wife,

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:01.560
